'''酪氨酸酶'''（{{lang-en|Tyrosinase}}）是一种[[氧化酶|氧化酶]]，且是调控[[黑色素|黑色素]]生成的[[速率控制步驟|限速]][[酶|酶]]。这种酶参与黑色素合成的两个反应：第一步将单酚羟基化为二酚，第二步将邻二酚氧化为邻二醌。邻二醌再经过几步反应后就变为黑色素<ref name="pmid21144881">{{cite journal | vauthors = Kumar CM, Sathisha UV, Dharmesh S, Rao AG, Singh SA | title = Interaction of sesamol (3,4-methylenedioxyphenol) with tyrosinase and its effect on melanin synthesis | journal = Biochimie | volume = 93 | issue = 3 | pages = 562–9 | date = Mar 2011 | pmc =  | doi = 10.1016/j.biochi.2010.11.014 | pmid = 21144881 }}</ref>。酪氨酸酶是一种含[[銅|銅]]的酶，存在于植物与动物组织中，催化生成由[[酪氨酸|酪氨酸]]氧化而来的黑色素以及其它色素，如使剥皮或切片的[[马铃薯|马铃薯]]暴露在空气中变黑<ref>{{cite journal|url = http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0031942298002076 | doi=10.1016/S0031-9422(98)00207-6 | volume=49 | issue=3 | title=Tyrosine and cysteine are substrates for blackspot synthesis in potato | year=1998 | journal=Phytochemistry | pages=703–707 | vauthors=Stevens LH, Davelaar E, Kolb RM, Pennings EJ, Smit NP}}</ref>。在皮肤[[黑素細胞|黑素細胞]]的[[黑色素体|黑色素体]]中能发现酪氨酸酶。在人类基因组中，酪氨酸酶由 ''TYR'' [[基因|基因]]编码<ref name="pmid3146546">{{cite journal | vauthors = Barton DE, Kwon BS, Francke U | title = Human tyrosinase gene, mapped to chromosome 11 (q14----q21), defines second region of homology with mouse chromosome 7 | journal = Genomics | volume = 3 | issue = 1 | pages = 17–24 | date = Jul 1988 | pmid = 3146546 | doi = 10.1016/0888-7543(88)90153-X }}</ref>。

